text: Ampatuyoc (possibly from Quechua hamp'atu frog, -yuq a suffix to indicate ownership, "the one with a frog (or frogs)") is a mountain in the Andes of Peru, about high. It is located in the Ayacucho Region, Víctor Fajardo Province, Sarhua District. ==References== Category:Mountains of Peru Category:Mountains of Ayacucho Region
title: Ampatuyoc (Ayacucho)
